Status: proof of concept. Also you'll need my Enbugger fork until
Enbugger::ebug is accepted upstream.

  # This uses AnyEvent, so go with twiggy

  builder {
    enable 'Scrutiny';
    $app;
  };

  # Now pass ?_scrutinize=1 to your app, and you'll get an inline debugger

